headline: ADM Delays Financial Statement as It Reviews Previous Reports
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Archer-Daniels-Midland Co. has delayed the release of its financial statement for the third quarter as the company works to restate previous reports. The shares fell in after-hours trading.
